## UI layout

### Window constraints

- `min-width: 450px`
- `max-width: 640px`
- Single column; body scrolls when many cards are open
- `catalog: false` floating widget

### Structure

```
PaymentsWindow (Tailwind className only)
├── Intro           first visit — Enter shop
├── Header          filter chips (left) · [ Mint NFT ✨ ] (right)
├── MachineList     scroll · cards per open tunnel
└── Ticker          micro-payment marquee (optional)
```

### Machine card (`MachineCard.tsx`)

Gacha cabinet with sketch ink borders, LED status pill, and expandable
micro-payment history.

**Card regions:**

| Region         | Content                                                      |
| -------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Header         | Status LED (`idle` / `running` / `completed`)                |
| Prize window   | Catalog `imageUrl` / `titleNFT` preview; hint text per phase |
| Progress       | Usage label + `spent / target` + animated bar                |
| Stats grid     | **Ticks**, **TPS**, **Unit** (microUnit)                     |
| History toggle | Collapsed by default; expands last ~24 ticks                 |
| Actions        | Start / Pause / Claim NFT / dismiss                          |

Prototype: `frontend/src/games/regularPayments/` (Tailwind + `SketchDefs` ink spans).

