## Locked decisions

| Question                   | Decision                                                               |
| -------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Stake token                | **MTPS**                                                               |
| Open deposit               | **10 MTPS** per machine (browser wallet)                               |
| Purchase stream            | **0.001 MTPS** × **1000 ticks** = **1 MTPS** to shop B                 |
| Max machines               | **No limit** per window                                                |
| On-chain surface           | **2 steps**: browser **open** + backend **`/settle`** (close + mint)   |
| Per-tick on-chain mint     | **Never** — would destroy TPS; mint only in settle                     |
| Settle payload cap         | **16 MB**; tunnel move counter stops at **50k** moves                  |
| NFT metadata               | Browser catalog; **3 fields** → single `mint_random_nft` Move fn       |
| Randomness                 | **Browser** picks catalog row on complete; no on-chain tier roll in v1 |
| Shop fee                   | **None** — shop B uses balance only to execute mint, no revenue share  |
| Auto-start stream on spawn | **No** — explicit **Start** on each card (demo may differ)             |

